Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是雪雪太貪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撿栗子撿個不停才弄得這麼晚的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是無可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫我家是大家庭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋媽媽太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不得不照料大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕個什麼勁兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是隻鳥罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個羽毛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:19.04,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,想找到 藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早上都不休息地反覆揮刀  真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是兒時養成的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且呢  不好好練習的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一有一天能離開這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個人我是無論如何都想贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腋下太松垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼  我去河邊洗臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能早點回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然希望行人無法回去  一直留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是打得稍稍重了點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安啊雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼早要到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在南邊和西邊的交界處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了看到了 雪乃我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鳥啊  藍色的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚我在南邊的森嶺撿栗子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回家的途中不經意間看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是至今還沒被人見到過真面目的那隻傳說中的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這個是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有很多別的擁有藍色羽毛的鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有可能是綾音故意塗上色做的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身為動物博士的我都沒看到過的羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有這麼美麗的羽毛的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很想見見它並和它成為朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  所以小鈴姐你也一起幫我找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不和行人說一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兔兔去把行人帶到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天還要去撿柴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別管了別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴去找藍鳥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虛幻的藍鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（Unidentified Mysterious Animal  未確認動物）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島上也有UMA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,未被確認的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還未被發現的新種類的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  對我來說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也稱得上是未知的珍獸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是行人你不是對不可靠的事物都持否定的態度嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,UMA和其他的是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在理論上是可以解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  聽說如果能抓住藍鳥就能獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來叫行人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一會再去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天必須去撿柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿小鈴沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然丟下了撿柴的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是雪雪硬把她帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙撿柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在行人正一個人撿著柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到藍鳥的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快開始搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有鷹鷹和貓頭鷹在就輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它們昨晚就和媽媽一起去山上泡溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回到家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只留下了「我們去溫泉了」的紙條
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡早上睡懶覺  早上喝酒和早上泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是一個廢柴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把女兒丟下不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就只靠我們幾個人找出藍鳥好好地炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憑藉這個氣味去找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似只是羽毛進了鼻子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為已經受潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天下了雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說小鈴  再到更深處去看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  小鈴沒有一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想一下的話  自從到了島上我們大多數時間都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說我給小鈴添了這麼多的麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都讓她這麼費心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都沒幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是輕易能找到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是所謂的虛幻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  能找到藍鳥的話就能帶來幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是童話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,童話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我小的時候千影姐姐經常讀給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  能帶來幸福只限於童話中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事我當然知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來只限於童話故事中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是與未知的動物交朋友這點不就足夠幸福了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是雪雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是藍鳥真的能帶來幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐想要怎樣的幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話  一直維持現在的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  只要大家都能健健康康的就算幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一塊的氣味很重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇到它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要悄悄地接近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虛幻的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是沒見過的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全都看不出是藍顏色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亂跑一氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小鳥  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飛就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有深溝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼晚才回來對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直找不到合適的柴火…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐你快起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃你早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說早安的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是悠閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 我們掉到深溝裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為雪雪暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能爬得上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,腳腫起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是掉下來的時候扭到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很痛的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 腳是這種情況要爬上去是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,邊緣太松了  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,邊緣比我想像的還要脆弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是行人的話  在這個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  已經讓兔兔去通知行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人應該已經察覺到我們出事了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會來找我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這裡可是森林的最深處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有發現這個洞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排鼻子很靈敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人腦袋很好使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  雪乃她們沒在小鈴家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴也沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道在山裡出了什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道會這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就帶他們一起去泡溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鏡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能冷靜的下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大家出了什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什麼不測  這是什麼話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全陷入混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情緒變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去山上找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鏡小姐就在村子裡找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野豬和貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去幫助行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天見到藍鳥的就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是小鈴她們身邊發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是在森林中迷路了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了炸豬排  到你出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照氣味去尋找小鈴她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小鈴那邊也有鼻子很靈的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是因為迷路的話不會回不來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是遇到了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天徹底黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶了櫻桃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我特地摘給行人和炸豬排的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家分著吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊  行人他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟去哪找了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐你還真沉著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我緊張地受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以前也有被困在洞中的情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候行人很沉著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想  要是我也能冷靜下來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也會有辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是和小鈴姐一起真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你什麼都會做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身材也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在我這個年紀已經在那個家裡獨自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想像小鈴姐那麼堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒有這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的氣味會被沖走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最糟的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排  野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雨聲太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音似乎也傳的不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴現在一定是忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:11.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才好像有誰在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你在叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是想讓我跟著你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道小鈴她們在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能給人帶來幸福的藍鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不相信這種迷信的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我小鈴在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會跟丟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是小鈴的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  我們在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人來救我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  藍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  到哪去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是幻影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不得安寧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然會掉到那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴也真是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛嘛  只要沒事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凜你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止再有人掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做一個柵欄之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為這個笨蛋才讓你遇到這麼大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是能再小心點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴還真是可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也給我學著點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  還真是個小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像我這樣綁根安全繩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是很危險的 綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也有一個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  一起吃我帶來慰問大家的溫泉饅頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你擔心真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受了傷不能隱瞞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別跟我這麼見外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是一家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  腳很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我變得孤零零的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都對我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而沒有一個人斥責過我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  行人你說我們是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我背你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴又小又輕啊
